title: The Performer
description:
It’s the eve of your wedding, and you fear you’ve made a huge mistake. Music is your passion, but you’re not sure your fiancée believes in your talent. There’s greatness in you, but it’s not even clear you’ll make it through the night. Hosted by Robbie Daymond.
